item.title: About
item.description: Yun is a data scientist based in the Netherlands. She does remote consulting/development for a range of companies and organisations. She’s also open to onsite work in the Netherlands. Technologies she likes to work with include Python (NumPy, Pandas, SciPy, Plotly, Matplotlib, etc) and SQL (PostgreSQL). You can see her other work on her personal site. For business inquiries please send an email.
